abstract: When Zulhumar Isaac’s parents disappeared amid a wave of detentions of ethnic minorities, she had to play a perilous game with the state to get them back.

abstract: The group spearheaded a commercially successful folk revival in the late 1950s and early ’60s, with Mr. Shane singing lead most of the time.
snippet: The group spearheaded a commercially successful folk revival in the late 1950s and early ’60s, with Mr. Shane singing lead most of the time.
lead_paragraph: Bob Shane, the last surviving original member of the Kingston Trio, whose smooth close harmonies helped transform folk music from a dusty niche genre into a dominant brand of pop music in the 1950s and ’60s, died on Sunday in Phoenix. He was 85.

abstract: Iowa caucusgoers aren’t just asking about the one issue that’s dominating the headlines.
snippet: Iowa caucusgoers aren’t just asking about the one issue that’s dominating the headlines.
lead_paragraph: MARSHALLTOWN, Iowa — With three jurors in the impeachment trial traipsing about Iowa this past weekend, you’d expect someone — anyone! — planning to attend the Iowa caucuses to ask the presidential candidates about impeachment.
